</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="170" pageNumber="773" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="170.[1366,2571,2105,2651]" pageId="170" pageNumber="773">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1366,1606,2464,2493]" pageId="170" pageNumber="773">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Hatt’s Thicket Rat is presumably nocturnal and crepuscular. It is scansorial (adapted for climbing).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
